<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5308063>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–26. Bochkovia phalaropi sp. n. Female. 15. Gnathosoma in ventral view. 16. Peritremes. 17. Ventral view of opisthosoma. 18. Propodonotal seta vi. 19. Solenidia of leg I. 20. Fan-like seta p’ of leg III. 21. Tarsus III in ventral view. Male. 22. Hypostomal apex in ventral view. 23. Peritremes. 24. Opisthosoma in dorsal view. 25. Tarsus III in latero-ventral view. 26. Fan-like seta p’ of leg III. Scale lines 20µm (Figs 15, 16 and 18–26), 50µm (Fig. 17)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5308063/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5308061>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13, 14. Bochkovia phalaropi sp. n. Female. 13. Dorsal view. 14. Ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5308061/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5308065>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27, 28. Bochkovia phalaropi sp. n. Male. 27. Dorsal view. 28. Ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5308065/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

